name: - Pressure -
description:
Deep in dark space, almost non-existent in this dimension, there are The Stellar Jellyfish, their tentacles form the fabric of existence and their bodies contain the galaxies where we live in.
It is said that getting a piece of their body can bestow eternal wisdom.
Some have tried to hunt the jellyfish without success, all of them have lost their heads on contact.
So don't you try it boy!! you wanna go mad????

Inktober 2021 collection on HEN

Day 9: Pressure
